ents it took us a long time to get the formula to be exactly what i had envisioned i believe that what we use on our hair is equally as important as what we put onto our skin and i felt there was a true need in the market for clean safe haircare that really works you shouldn’t have to sacrifice performance to get products you trust” related photos the best ombré hair of all time she can’t choose just one favorite product “i love them all but i would have to say that my favorites for everyday use are the beyond hydrated shampoo beyond hydrated conditioner moisture milk leavein conditioner and the sea salt spray these are my goto products for that effortless texture look i am also really excited about the dry condition  shine serum it gives your hair a polished shine without adding weight” she only washes her roots “i don’t have a lot of time to spend getting ready in the morning i typically shampoo my roots and condition the rest of my hair” she’s a master at creating her own bouncy waves “i’ve been getting my hair and makeup done professionally since i was  so i’ve had the chance to learn from some of the best stylists i love a wavy hair look when i’m out of the shower i towel dry and spray leavein conditioner which is amazing and then i use our volumizing spray and sea salt spray i shake dry my hair with a blow dryer then i take different size chunks and wrap my hair around a curling iron leaving the ends out i go in different directions throughout my hair so the waves are a little messy and effortless” courtesy honest beautycourtesy honest beauty her friends tested all of her products “one of the most important things for me was that these products actually performed i had a lot of my friends people at the office and professional hairstylists test out the products we wanted to make sure that they would work for everyone and that they would hold a style from the office to the red carpet” her hair routine has changed drastically since creating her own line “i no longer have to spend time searching for products that won’t give me allergies i finally have products that i absolutely love and products that do everything i need them to do” have you tried any of her new products sound off below show full article most popular  model lucky blue smith and former miss teen usa stormi bree welcome daughter gravity  stephanie seymour  poses nude for love magazine  tara reid goes braless in seethrough chainmail mini dress  sarah hyland on building body confidence in costar ariel winter ‘i tried to be a true older sister’  jennifer aniston on her sensual new scent her forever datenight fragrance and more see also send to email address your name your email address cancel post was not sent  check your email addresses email check failed please try again sorry your blog cannot share posts by email jessica albas honest hair products what to know people close subscribe stay connected facebook tumblr instagram pinterest youtube snapchat subscribe print magazine all access premium free trial gift box offer give a gift buy current issue customer service advertise with us online magazine learn more more special offers mobile apps sitemap contact us privacy policy your california privacy rights terms of service ad choices copyright   time inc all rights reserved reproduction in whole or in part without permission is prohibited skip to content facebook tumblr instagram pinterest youtube snapchat stylejessica alba’s allergies mean you now get healthy hair careby jillian ruffo•jillianruffoposted on august   at pm edt sharetweetemail pinterest if you already did one big beauty bag purge to make way for jessica alba‘s honest beauty makeup and skincare products it’s time to dump everything out of your medicine cabinet to make room for her hair products the mother of two has just released a haircare line and it contains everything you need — from shampoo to salt spray — and ranges from  at ulta and honestbeautycom below see everything alba has to say about t