ir oil and root lift as the products shes been experimenting with and loving from the lineyou may also likehairthe best haircare routine according to your hair concernhairshould i shave my head to make my hair grow back healthieras for her instructions i do the seasalt spray at the root and i use conditioning milk at the ends then i scrunch right before its completely dry ill mist with the oil its awesome we have a hair oil thats like a mist she said she recently put them all to the test at the dior show at paris fashion week and for the vanity fair oscar party the hairdresser used our root lift and all the other products and it held the whole time they really work they really hold and they smell amazing as with most of the other scents in the line the fragrances of the hair products are inspired by albas favorite vacation spots and the familiar scents of her childhoodi tried digging for more information but thats all she would divulge when i reached out to her team for a comment they could only confirm that the line will launch in october and they would keep us posted so sit tight be patient and look forward to finally having all the ingredients to achieving jessica albas enviable waves at homego backstage at new york fashion week with mac senior artist keri blairwatch this video on the scenekeywordsjessica albabeachy waveshair productskeywordsjessica albabeachy waveshair productsfacebook dialogpinterestemailcollectionshot rollersbouncy voluminous curls for every texturebuy itreadreviewtt volumizing hot rollers luxebuy itreadreviewdovedove oxygen moisture leave in foamreadreviewjohn friedajohn frieda styling tools by conair body  shine smooth wavesreadreviewliving proofliving proof hold flexible hairspraybuy itreadreviewconairconair styling essentials thermal selfgrip rollersin the newsa salon employee is facing backlash after temporarily banning men while cutting a muslim womans hairthe employee reportedly hung a sign reading no men pleasejuly 8 stand the heatthes